opinions
I actually don't know what to say since i don't know you that well, your yt channel is fine and you're a good player (or hacker :thinking:) (that was a joke pls no h8)

opinions on avicus
The server has potential which is never used, the owners do work but when the community has a suggestion/complaint they're often ignored, and they're the ones with all the power so we can't just contact another higher up with suggestions they can't do much about. The community is alright, some parts of the staff team are sinking (dev, mapdev) but they're trying to get back up, social media is getting reformed and I want it to go well, moderation staff is fine and event staff are cool :P

avicus or stratus
That depends on many factors. Maps on Stratus are better, it has more players, a more organized staff team, etc but atm Avicus is a lot less laggy than Stratus (for me), i like both communities equally and I feel that the avicus staff team is more chill than the stratus one.
